                    <h2 class="section-heading"><span class="section-number">04</span>Layout Comparison: Choosing the Right Framework</h2>
                    <p>The right layout is not an aesthetic preference — it is a strategic decision based on your studio's business model, portfolio depth, and target client profile. The table below compares the three frameworks across the dimensions that drive conversion for high-value architecture commissions. Use it to identify your starting point, then adapt from there.</p>

